  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0dd4. \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db1 205\u0d9a \u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca \u0db6\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca\u0d9a\u0da7\u0dca \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Rs. 205 million gold biscuits seized",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Officers of the Customs Narcotics Control Division at the airport arrival terminal of an air passenger and a maid of the airport duty free shopping mall who tried to take out of Katunayake airport a consignment of gold biscuits worth 205 million rupees (205 million rupees) weighing 09 kg and 500 grams. A group has been arrested this morning.",
        "He is a 39-year-old airline passenger residing in Nittambuwa area. He had arrived at Katunayake Airport at 08.35 this morning from Dubai on Emirates Airlines flight EK-650. The woman who has been arrested is a 38-year-old woman from Seeduwa who was employed at the Katunayake Airport duty-free shopping complex.",
        "The passenger was arrested by the officials of the Customs Narcotics Control Division while attempting to leave the Katunayake airport after hiding 80 gold biscuits in his luggage and the maid in her hand bag.",
        "At present, the two are under arrest and the airport customs officers are conducting further investigations on this matter."
      ],
